
Inform 6.15 for Atari XL/XE
---------------------------

This is Inform 6.15, the last release that supported Z-machine version 3
suitable for 8-bit micros.  This port specifically aims to produce
playable Atari XL/XE MD disk images.

It is using mInform 1.1 library.

Building
--------

Read Makefile.  In most scenarios you just need to issue:

  $ make
  $ make install

Usage
-----

  $ i6 game.inf

This will create game.z3 and game.atr.

